channel.title: Logitech Gaming Software
channel.description: Hey guys, was wondering if you might have some insight to help me here. I'm trying to install the Logitech Gaming Software to configure my mouse, and it's binds. Whenever I try to run the installer, it just opens up my user folder (users>"myname.exe") instead of actually installing the software. Any ideas on how to actually get it installed? I'm a little stumped. Am I missing something really obvious? Thanks in advance!
